pipeline-mod-celia v1.2.0
=========================

Includes
--------
- Aggregate letter- and word-spacing under letter-spacing in UI
- Default behavior for undefined characters: Replace with an asterisk
- Add copyright and trademark symbols to translation tables
- Implement default behaviour for simple tables
- Add preprocessing step for tables containing forward slashes
- Support for certain line elements too long to fit on one line: <tr>, <line>, <li>
- Support for <noteref> elements
- Add .notransform class for UTF-8 Braille content that is to be passed through the system unchanged

pipeline-mod-celia v1.1.0
=========================

Includes
--------
- Support for letter- and word-spacing

pipeline-mod-celia v1.0.0
=========================

Includes
--------
- Improved hyphenation table for Finnish (https://github.com/snaekobbi/issues/issues/2)
- Custom Liblouis based translator that handles `html:strong` and `html:em`
  (https://github.com/snaekobbi/liblouis/issues/1, https://github.com/snaekobbi/issues/issues/13,
  https://github.com/snaekobbi/issues/issues/14, https://github.com/snaekobbi/pipeline-mod-braille/issues/38)
